==History==
{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}
{{History|1.1|Added [[Mill]], [[Shed]], and [[Farmhouse|Farmhouse upgrade 3]] for purchase. Added ability for [[Robin]] to move placed buildings through the construction menu. Introduced a number of new [[furniture]] objects to rotating stock.}}
{{History|1.3.27|Added [[Shipping|Shipping Bin]], [[Cabin]]s, and "[[Trailer|Community Upgrade]]" to construction menu. Added price increase for wood and stone in Year 2. Added [[Basic Log]], [[Log Section]], [[Brick Fireplace]], [[Stone Fireplace]], and [[Stove Fireplace]] to permanent stock.}}
{{History|1.4|Added [[Fish Pond]] and [[Shed|Big Shed]] to construction menu. Added [[Workbench]], [[Wood Chipper]], [[Mini-Fridge]], and [[Brick Floor]] (Recipe) to permanent stock. Dressers' prices increased from {{Price|1000}} to {{Price|5000}} ([[Mahogany Dresser]] from {{Price|2000}} to {{Price|7500}}). Flooring blueprints' prices reduced ([[Wood Floor]], [[Stone Floor]], & [[Stepping Stone Path]] from {{Price|500}} to {{Price|100}}; [[Straw Floor]] & [[Crystal Path]] from {{Price|1000}} to {{Price|200}})}}
{{History|1.5|Added [[Carpenter's Shop#House Renovations|House Renovations]] and [[Carpenter's Shop#Town shortcuts|second Community Upgrade]]. Added [[Carpenter's Shop#Painting|Paint Buildings]] to construction menu. Added [[Telephone]], [[Single Bed|Bed]], [[Double Bed]], [[Child Bed]], and [[Deluxe Red Double Bed]] to permanent stock. Added [[Colorful Set]] to rotating stock. The [[Greenhouse]] can now be moved once restored. The default [[Shipping|Shipping Bin]] next to the farmhouse can now be moved or demolished. Reduced Workbench price from {{Price|3000}} to {{Price|2000}}.}}
{{History|1.5.5|Buildings can now be placed on [[Artifact Spot|artifact spots]]. They are destroyed in the process.}}
{{History|1.6|Increased price for the second house upgrade from {{Price|50000}} to {{Price|65000}}, but reduced [[Hardwood]] required from 150 to 100. [[Slime Hutch]] now has a smaller size of 7x4. Braziers can now be bought in any order. [[Cabin]]s no longer cost materials, just {{Price|100}}. Most renovations are no longer free. Added new renovation options. You can now build pet bowls in [[Robin]]'s shop, with three variants. Construction time is now visible when constructing farm buildings.}}

